<h4 id="product-overview">Product Overview</h4>

<p style="text-align:justify">With a Sleek, Shiny, unique design Realme 2 offers long-lasting battery life and smooth user experience. Packed up with  64 GB of internal storage space you have enough space for storing all your pictures, music, and more. This Realme 2 has a glossy finish that reflects light gives you a great experience while streaming videos. Call more, tap more, and play more with your smartphone with expanded battery life(4230mAh - AI Power Master). Access Your Phone at a Glance with Quick Facial &amp; Fingerprint Unlock. The Powerful Processor Snapdragon Octa-core CPU enables you to facilitate multitasking effortlessly. </p>

